ters say that vibrant street life is part of the capital's character.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"supporters\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"vibrant street life\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital's character\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The summer terraces are seen as an extension of the historic pavement seating areas that have been a feature of Parisian bars and restaurants for centuries.\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The summer terraces\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"an extension\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"the historic pavement seating areas\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"a feature\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisian bars\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"centuries\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Frederic Hocquard, the deputy mayor in charge of the night-time economy, said the city had made a \\\"social and festive choice\\\" in allowing the terraces to stay open later during the Olympics which begin on July 28.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Frederic Hocquard\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"the deputy mayor\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"the night-time economy\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"social and festive choice\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"the terraces\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1721}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added that they helped \\\"regulate public space at night\\\" and made streets safer.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public space\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"streets\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Games, the first time the Olympics have been held in the City of Light in a century, have been hit by controversies in recent months over the price of tickets and transport, as well as the official poster.\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 2085, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paris Games\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"a century\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"controversies\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1995}, {\"ngram\": \"recent months\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"the price\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"transport\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"the official poster\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French organisers and the International Olympic Committee (IOC) have played them down as typical issues before the event.\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999095037194721, \"rank\": 8.81377557852672e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"tex